description:
Muzika komedio pri amo de baletistino kaj opera kantisto, kun multaj scenoj el baletoj de Chajkovskij. Kun subtitoloj en Esperanto. Vd. pli detale che: http://kinejo.blogsome.com/2007/07/17/la-baleta-solistino/

The Ballet Soloist (also known as Russian Ballerina) is a musical melodrama about love of ballerina and opera singer, with scenes from Tchaikovski&amp;#039;s Swan Lake and Sleeping Beauty. Great Russian ballerina Galina Ulanova plays in first ballet episode of the film. With internal subtitles in Esperanto.

